17:04.358 --> 17:06.193
Wait a second, what's your name?

17:06.734 --> 17:08.362
Sylvia Plath.

17:10.821 --> 17:14.660
It might say that I'm dead
but that's another Sylvia Plath.

17:14.660 --> 17:16.036
I scrubbed all my shit.

17:16.036 --> 17:18.955
You're very pale.
You want ten minutes in the tanning bed?

17:18.955 --> 17:20.332
No, I'm good.

17:21.124 --> 17:23.001
What do you think happened to Donatella?

17:23.836 --> 17:25.712
I don't know. She split.

17:25.712 --> 17:28.464
This you? <i>The Bell Jar</i> book?

17:28.464 --> 17:32.386
No, that's the dead Sylvia.
That book's a downer.

17:32.386 --> 17:34.471
So you don't think somebody killed her?

17:34.471 --> 17:38.141
- Like her husband?
- Her husband?

17:38.141 --> 17:39.226
That guy? No.

17:40.102 --> 17:42.896
- So, not the husband Bob?
- No, Dona. No.

17:42.896 --> 17:46.525
Fuck me, Daddy. What did you do?
Fuck me, sailor.

17:46.525 --> 17:48.735
- Fuck. Fuck.
- Bird's got a mouth on it.

17:48.735 --> 17:50.696
Goes off every time he hears his name.

17:51.488 --> 17:53.991
- Bob's?
