17:54.491 --> 17:56.702
- She had that thing forever.
- Fuck me, sailor.

17:57.244 --> 18:00.622
Anyway,
that guy's a granola-eating fruitcake.

18:00.622 --> 18:02.374
- Couldn't do it.
- I don't know.

18:02.374 --> 18:05.085
He's pretty buff.
From the pictures I've seen.

18:05.085 --> 18:09.673
You know, powerful in his own way.
But he could kill.

18:10.299 --> 18:11.300
Nah.

18:11.925 --> 18:15.512
